{"_path":"/blog/car-that-conquered-world","_dir":"blog","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"The Car That Conquered the World: Our Trusted Companion","description":"Meet the remarkable vehicle that carried us around the globe twice, through extreme conditions and across six continents. The unsung hero of our world records.","date":"2024-01-20","author":"Saloo Chowdhury","category":"Technical Stories","featured":false,"image":"/images/blog/our-car.jpg","tags":["car","vehicle","technical","reliability","engineering"],"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"the-car-that-conquered-the-world-our-trusted-companion"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Car That Conquered the World: Our Trusted Companion"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Behind every great adventure is a reliable companion. For our record-breaking circumnavigations, that companion wasn't just Neena and me - it was our remarkable car that carried us safely around the world not once, but twice."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"choosing-the-right-vehicle"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Choosing the Right Vehicle"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Selecting the right car for circumnavigating the globe wasn't a decision we took lightly. We needed a vehicle that could handle:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Extreme temperature variations (-40°C to +50°C)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Diverse road conditions (from German autobahns to African dirt tracks)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"High-speed sustained driving for weeks"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Limited maintenance opportunities"}]},{"type":"eleme